legacy.full_text: #Hangzhou, the host city of the upcoming #AsianGames, is famed for its beautiful West Lake filled with lotuses. Two stadiums for the Games have drawn on this beauty, using unfolding lotus petals as inspiration, an amazing blend of natural beauty and architecture. #ChineseRomance https://t.co/xBZkuyRhNF
These lotus-shaped venues are super artistic works! So excited that the big event is just around the corner!! 😃😃
